    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted given the COU scope is limited to the single ASTM F1717 static compression-bending configuration and the remaining factors provide sufficient confidence in model predictions. Model risk level 3 with medium assurance level is consistent with Class II device regulatory pathway.",
